OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome early
OL,6,Fevening bright spells possible before
OL,7,Fcloud and rain, this perhaps heavy at
OL,8,Ftimes, spreads to all parts through
OL,9,Fthe night. Breezy, especially on
OL,10,Fcoasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,13,Frain, heavy at times, this slowly
OL,14,Fclearing away eastwards later. Some
OL,15,Flate brightness developing, along with
OL,16,Fa chance of showers. Winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
