OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStrong
OL,6,Fwinds Sunday, with rain spreading
OL,7,Feast. Breezy Monday with bright spells
OL,8,Fbut mostly dry until later. Becoming
OL,9,Fdry but cloudy and breezy on Tuesday.
OL,10,FTemperatures a little above average.
